[Tier2UpgradeComponents X2ItemTemplate]
FriendlyName="Upgrade Component (Tier 2)"
FriendlyNamePlural="Upgrade Components (Tier 2)"
BriefSummary="These pieces of alien magnetic weaponry are still intact and will do wonders when we want to adapt their tech for our own equipment."

[Tier3UpgradeComponents X2ItemTemplate]
FriendlyName="Upgrade Component (Tier 3)"
FriendlyNamePlural="Upgrade Components (Tier 3)"
BriefSummary="These pieces of alien beam weapon technology are still intact. We can use them to adapt their tech for our own equipment."

[Medikit X2WeaponTemplate]
FriendlyName="First Aid Kit"
FriendlyNamePlural="First Aid Kits"
BriefSummary="The Aid Kit contains a pressurized solution that, when exposed to air, acts as a sealant and insulator. Infused with painkillers and antiseptics, the Medikit can treat wounds and remove a variety of adverse conditions, including burns and poison."
TacticalText="<Bullet/> A Medikit can restore <Ability:MEDIKITPERUSEHP/>HP to a single soldier.\n<Bullet/> A Medikit can also be used to remove Burning, Acid, and Poison effects from any soldier.\n<Bullet/> A Medikit can also be used to stabilize a soldier that is bleeding out.\n<Bullet/>A Medikit only has a single charge, and if used on allies, they must be in an adjacent tile.\n<Bullet/> Does not affect robotic allies.\n"

[NanoMedikit X2WeaponTemplate]
FriendlyName="Nano Aid Kit"
FriendlyNamePlural="Nano Aid Kits"
BriefSummary="The Nano Aid Kit represents a substantial upgrade over our standard Medikit, increasing the health restored to injured soldiers."
TacticalText="<Bullet/> A Nanomedikit can restore <Ability:NANOMEDIKITHEALHP/>HP to a single soldier.\n<Bullet/> Like the base Medikit, a Nanomedikit can remove negative environmental effects from soldiers and can stabilize soldiers that are bleeding out.\n<Bullet/> Does not affect robotic allies.\n"

[NanofiberVest X2EquipmentTemplate]
FriendlyName="Sealed Nanoscale Vest"
FriendlyNamePlural="Sealed Nanoscale Vests"
BriefSummary="A light armor improvement derived from ADVENT armor. This item can be worn with all XCOM armors to increase soldier health and to provide immunity to poison."
TacticalText="<Bullet/> Grants a small but possibly decisive boost to soldier health.\n<Bullet/> Provides immunity to poison.\n<Bullet/> Only one armor enhancement can be equipped at a time."
